details.name: Void
details.description: Creates a damaging void that slows an enemy unit and deals damage.  Void also mini-stuns, interrupting channeling abilities. The slowing effect lasts longer at night. Deals half damage during day. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Causes Void to be an AoE ability. Increases the ministun duration and reduces cooldown.
